  "description": "This individual is a broad-shouldered human of middle years, with brown eyes set beneath a heavy brow and a blunt, work-worn nose. Black hair is kept in a neat parted style that exposes a squared hairline and prominent temples. Taupe skin shows ingrained fine lines at the eyes and mouth, consistent with long hours in lamplight and smoke. The hands are large and callused, with thickened knuckles and faint burn marks that record a career of hot kettles, glass, and spilled spirits.",
